05:32.598 --> 05:36.468
<font color="#804040">MAN</font>: Guys. Tomorrow, thank you.

05:36.469 --> 05:38.970
- <font color="#808080">(SIGHS)</font>
- MAN: Good night, boys.

05:38.971 --> 05:41.406
<font color="#808080">(MITCH COUGHING)</font>
I fucking hate Tequila!

05:41.407 --> 05:42.908
