gonna wake-up complete, my friend.

06:01.291 --> 06:01.827
That's right.

06:01.828 --> 06:03.428
- Thank you. Thank you.
- I helped.

06:03.429 --> 06:05.063
Complete.

06:05.064 --> 06:06.431
