06:19.846 --> 06:22.948
- <i>To accept this call, press 1.</i>
- <font color="#808080">(GROANS)</font>

06:22.949 --> 06:25.516
- <font color="#804040">MAN #2</font>: <i>Everything okay?</i>
- Yeah.

06:27.152 --> 06:30.455
Yeah. Ugh. See you tomorrow.

06:30.456 --> 06:32.524
Listen, when you throw up
in the middle of the night,

06:32.525 --> 06:34.493
- aim away from your baby.
- Yeah, I will.

06:34.494 --> 06:36.094
- Aim away from the baby.
- MITCH: Away from the baby.

06:36.095 --> 06:37.119
<font color="#804040">MITCH</font>: I promise.

06:37.120 --> 06:39.798
<font color="#804040">MAN #2</font>: Don't puke on
your child, Mitch.

06:39.799 --> 06:42.134
- I won't puke on my child.
- MAN: Until tomorrow.

06:42.135 --> 06:43.601
<font color="#804040">MITCH</font>: Tomorrow.

06:44.936 --> 06:46.171
<font color="#804040">MAN</font>: Don't be late!

06:46.172 --> 06:48.940
<i><font color="#808080">(LINE RINGS)</font>
</i>

06:48.941 --> 06:50.776
